<a href="/questions/36-does-this-book-make-anybody-else-think">Does this book make anybody else think Capitalism is f*cked up?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_36'><a id="like_count_community_question_36" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/36?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">17 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F24724602-flash-boys">like</a></span>

