<span id="freeTextContainer6192857847293184893">Excellent. Reads like a novel but is all real. There is a lot of detail and a lot of characters. I have not read any other book from Michael Lewis but if this is his style it is worth recommending. Its amazing how everything collude and how the small don&apos;t stand a chance. You cannot argue that alongside politicians, bankers and money brokers everywhere (not just wall street) are in this world for themselves (with few exceptions) no matter what, but I guess that is nothing new.</span>
