<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7495395-the-quants"><img alt="The Quants: How a New Breed of Math Whizzes Conquered Wall Street and Nearly Destroyed It" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1320432894l/7495395._SX98_.jpg" />
