<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer9595923721485990405"><strong>Michael Lewis</strong>, the best-selling author of <em>Liar’s Poker</em>, <em>The Money Culture</em>, <em>The New New Thing</em>, <em>Moneyball</em>, <em>The Blind Side</em>, <em>Panic</em>, <em>Home Game</em>, <em>The Big Short</em>, and <em>Boomerang</em>, among other works, lives in Berkeley, California, with his wife and three children.</span>

</div>
